2. **tests/test_generated_tariff.py:49** — `test_sunday_free_during_peak_hours` (Scenario T-H11)
3. **tests/test_generated_tariff.py:76** — `test_weekday_rules[5-7-expected5]` (Scenario T-H10 parametrized)
4. **tests/test_generated_tariff.py:76** — `test_weekday_rules[6-7-expected6]` (Scenario T-H11 parametrized)
5. **tests/test_tariff.py:18** — `test_sunday_is_free_all_day` (existing baseline test)

